if ( YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_is_interactive ) \
                { \
                int c = '*'; \
                size_t n; \
                for ( n = 0; n < max_size && \
                             (c = getc( utap_in )) != EOF && c != '\n'; ++n ) \
                        buf[n] = (char) c; \
                if ( c == '\n' ) \
                        buf[n++] = (char) c; \
                if ( c == EOF && ferror( utap_in ) ) \
                        YY_FATAL_ERROR( "input in flex scanner failed" ); \
                result = n; \
                } \
        else \
                { \
                errno=0; \
                while ( (result = fread(buf, 1, max_size, utap_in))==0 && ferror(utap_in)) \
                        { \
                        if( errno != EINTR) \
                                { \
                                YY_FATAL_ERROR( "input in flex scanner failed" ); \
                                break; \
                                } \
                        errno=0; \
                        clearerr(utap_in); \
                        } \
